title: Rubber Tires 1927 (American silent film comedy) Bessie Love, Erwin Connelly, Frank Coghlan Jr.

sources.title: Rubber Tires 1927 (American silent film comedy) Bessie Love, Erwin Connelly, Frank Coghlan Jr.
sources.description:
A hilarious picture comedy of "tin can" tourists.
The Stack family of New York City has fallen on difficult financial times. Pa Stack squandered the family's money by buying a home in Newhall, California, hoping that there would be oil on the land.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/biD9BFDzl-w


Original title: Rubber Tires (1927) AKA: Ten Thousand Reward

Director: Alan Hale
Writer: Frank Condon, Tay Garnett, Zelda Sears
Stars: Bessie Love, Erwin Connelly, Frank Coghlan Jr.
Genres: Silent film, Adventure, Comedy
